ender\", \"from\": 288, \"to\": 298}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif's lawyer, Nabil Boudi,announced on social medialast week that the boxing champion had filed a complaint for online harassment, calling it \\\"a new fight: that of justice, dignity and honor.\\\"\", \"from\": 304, \"to\": 499, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Khelif's lawyer\", \"from\": 304, \"to\": 319}, {\"ngram\": \"Nabil Boudi\", \"from\": 321, \"to\": 332}, {\"ngram\": \"social medialast week\", \"from\": 346, \"to\": 367}, {\"ngram\": \"the boxing champion\", \"from\": 373, \"to\": 392}, {\"ngram\": \"a complaint\", \"from\": 403, \"to\": 414}, {\"ngram\": \"online harassment\", \"from\": 419, \"to\": 436}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"a new fight\", \"from\": 449, \"to\": 461}, {\"ngram\": \"justice\", \"from\": 471, \"to\": 478}, {\"ngram\": \"dignity\", \"from\": 480, \"to\": 487}, {\"ngram\": \"honor\", \"from\": 492, \"to\": 497}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The criminal investigation will determine who initiated this misogynistic, racist and sexist campaign, but will also have to focus on those who fueled this digital lynching,\\\" Boudi said on social media.\", \"from\": 501, \"to\": 704, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The criminal investigation\", \"from\": 502, \"to\": 528}, {\"ngram\": \"this misogynistic, racist and sexist campaign\", \"from\": 558, \"to\": 603}, {\"ngram\": \"this digital lynching\", \"from\": 653, \"to\": 674}, {\"ngram\": \"Boudi\", \"from\": 677, \"to\": 682}, {\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 691, \"to\": 703}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The unfair harassment suffered by the boxing champion will remain the biggest stain on these Olympic Games.\\\"\", \"from\": 705, \"to\": 814, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The unfair harassment\", \"from\": 706, \"to\": 727}, {\"ngram\": \"the boxing champion\", \"from\": 740, \"to\": 759}, {\"ngram\": \"the biggest stain\", \"from\": 772, \"to\": 789}, {\"ngram\": \"these Olympic Games